How can we list the information of the blocked devices(partitions, HDD) on linux?

1. lsblk â€“ List Block Devices

lsblk -o NAME,SIZE,TYPE,MOUNTPOINT,FSTYPE,MODEL

lsblk -f

2. blkid â€“ Block Device Attributes

sudo blkid

3. fdisk -l â€“ Partition Table Listing

sudo fdisk -l


